cs]], 1974)\n* ''[[Ella and Oscar]]'' (Pablo, 1975)\n* ''[[Happy Time]]'' (Pablo, 1975) with [[Roy Eldridge]]\n* ''[[Oscar Peterson and the Bassists \u2013 Montreux '77]]'' (Pablo, 1977)\n* ''[[Eddie \"Lockjaw\" Davis 4 \u2013 Montreux '77]]'' (Pablo, 1977)\n* ''[[How Long Has This Been Going On? (Sarah Vaughan album)|How Long Has This Been Going On?]]'' [[Sarah Vaughan]] (Pablo, 1978)\n* ''[[The Trumpet Summit Meets the Oscar Peterson Big 4]]'' (Pablo, 1980) ([[Dizzy Gillespie]], [[Freddie Hubbard]], [[Clark Terry]])\n* ''[[The Alternate Blues]]'' (Pablo, 1980), Dizzy Gillespie, Freddie Hubbard, Clark Terry\n* ''[[Ain't But a Few of Us Left]]'' (Palbo, 1981) Milt Jackson, Ray Brown, [[Grady Tate]]\n* ''[[Live at the Blue Note (Oscar Peterson album)|Live at the Blue Note]]'' ([[Telarc International Corporation|Telarc]], 1990)\n* ''[[Saturday Night at the Blue Note]]'' (Telarc, 1990)\n* ''[[Last Call at the Blue Note]]'' (Telarc, 1990)\n* ''[[Encore at the Blue Note]]'' (Telarc, 1990)\n* ''[[Side by Side (Oscar Peterson and Itzhak Perlman album)|Side by Side]]'' (Telarc, 1994)\n* ''[[The More I See You (album)|The More I See You]]'', [[Benny Carter]], Clark Terry (Telarc, 1995)\n* ''[[A Tribute to Oscar Peterson \u2013 Live at the Town Hall]]'' (Telarc, 1997)\n* ''[[Oscar and Benny]]'' (Telarc, 1998)\n'''With [[Andr\u00e9 Previn]]'''\n* ''[[Old Friends (Andr\u00e9 Previn album)|Old Friends]]''\n* ''[[Uptown (Andr\u00e9 Previn album)|Uptown]]''\n* ''[[After Hours (Andr\u00e9 Previn album)|After Hours]]''\n* ''[[What Headphones?]]''\n* ''[[Andr\u00e9 Previn and Friends Play Show Boat]]'' ([[Deutsche Grammophon]], 1995)\n'''With Andr\u00e9 Previn and [[Kiri Te Kanawa]]'''\n* ''[[Kiri Sidetracks: The Jazz Album]]''\n'''With [[Buddy Rich]]'''\n* ''[[The Wailing Buddy Rich]]'' (Norgran, 1955)\n'''With [[Red Rodney]]'''\n*''[[Superbop]]'' (Muse, 1974)\n'''With [[Lalo Schifrin]]'''\n* ''[[Music from Mission: Impossible]]'' ([[Dot Records|Dot]], 1967)\n* ''[[There's a Whole L